# Study Guide: Unit 1 - Introduction to Data Communication and Computer Networks

## Table of Contents
- [Overview](#overview)
- [Key Concepts](#key-concepts)
- [Historical Milestones](#historical-milestones)
- [Data Communication](#data-communication)
- [Defining a Network](#defining-a-network)
